{"name":"Seed&Spark","permalink":"seed-spark","crunchbase_url":"http://www.crunchbase.com/company/seed-spark","homepage_url":"http://www.seedandspark.com","blog_url":"http://seedandspark.tumblr.com/","blog_feed_url":"","twitter_username":"seedandspark","category_code":"games_video","number_of_employees":null,"founded_year":2012,"founded_month":null,"founded_day":null,"deadpooled_year":null,"deadpooled_month":null,"deadpooled_day":null,"deadpooled_url":null,"tag_list":"film, crowdsourcing, crowdfunding, entertainment","alias_list":null,"email_address":"hello@seedandspark.com","phone_number":"(347) 715-2987","description":"Crowdsourced film funding & distribution","created_at":"Wed Dec 05 15:56:11 UTC 2012","updated_at":"Thu Dec 06 06:00:31 UTC 2012","overview":"<p>Seed&amp;Spark, the first end-to-end solution for independent films to fund, produce, and distribute their films using the power of the crowd.</p>\n\n<p>The Seed&amp;Spark site is building a truly independent filmmaking community where filmmakers and audiences come together for crowd-funding, production, and streaming distribution. </p>\n\n<p>The site offers film projects that seek funding through crowdsourced cash and in-kind donations (Seed&amp;Spark Studio)and a slate of ‘ready-to-view’ independent films (Seed&amp;Spark Cinema).</p>\n\n<p>Film projects span all genres, from narrative features, comedies, documentaries and animations to experimental shorts. </p>\n\n<p>Every time an audience member supports the making of a moving picture project (funding, following, sharing) they earn “Sparks” which can be redeemed to watch movies on the streaming platform.</p>\n\n<p>The basic formula: crowd-funding platform + streaming platform = the future of filmmaking. </p>\n\n<p>The following video provides an overview of Seed&amp;Spark, produced indie-style by the Seed&amp;Spark team, http://vimeo.com/53617776</p>","image":{"available_sizes":[[[150,45],"assets/images/resized/0022/4002/224002v2-max-150x150.png"],[[250,